title: some of my calls are not coming through
content: I have notices that when I make calls (sometimes), they call will not go through. Also, when people try to call me, my phone will not ring/pick up the call.  This is starting to happen more frequently. It as gotten to the point where people will e-mail/Text me saying that they are trying to call and they are not able to get though.  I got this phone from Google two months ago.
